            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e00164-Hd1e108">Rubrica 18</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e00164-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De aciebus et ordinibus exeritus disponendis</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00164-d1e114">
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00164-d1e121">
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00164-d1e198"> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00164-d1e261"> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00164-d1e273"> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00164-d1e289"> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00164-d1e318"> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00164-d1e365"> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00164-d1e379"> 
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00164-Rd1e398"></ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00164-Qd1e381">manus de<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>fendere 
              illam perniciosius denudabis 
              <lb ed="#C"/>Si bellatorum tibi copia non habun<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>dat 
              melius <sic>melius</sic> est aciem habere breui<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>orem  
              dummodo in subsidiis colloces pluri<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>mos 
              nam circa medias partes campi 
              <lb ed="#C"/>ex peditibus bene armatis debes habere e<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>lectissimos 
              de quibus cunctum facias contra 
              <lb ed="#C"/>cornua autem de comatis loricatis<del>b</del> equi<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>tibus 
              ad hec seruatis ad leua armatura 
              <lb ed="#C"/>peditum alas hostium conueniet contingit</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00164-d1e453"> 
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00164-Rd1e474">Idem 13 titulo</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00164-Qd1e455">Obseruandum est ne sub ip<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>so 
              quo committitur pugna uelis ordines 
              <lb ed="#C"/>commutare aut de locis suis aliquos 
              <lb ed="#C"/>uniuersos numeros ad alia transferre statim 
              <lb ed="#C"/>enim nascitur tumultus atque confusio atque 
              <lb ed="#C"/><sic>Inperatores</sic> conturbatos facilius hostis 
              <lb ed="#C"/>inuadit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00164-d1e472"> 
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00164-Rd1e495">Idem 26 titulo et finali</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00164-Qd1e474">melius 
              <lb ed="#C"/>est post aciem plura seruare subsidia quam latius 
              <lb ed="#C"/>milites spargere qui dispersi suis inconsulte 
              <lb ed="#C"/>loquitur sequitur quam acceperat aduersa<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>rio 
              uult dare uictoriam</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
